data.description: ***WEST LANCASTER 4 BEDROOM 2 BATH POOL HOME! ***  When you walk in the front door you will see a spacious open-concept lay out, living room, dining room, huge family room with a brick fire place and sliding doors to the outdoor enclosed patio. Kitchen features granite countertops, white cabinets, and tile flooring. Guest bathroom displays unique pedestal sink and tile flooring. Primary bedroom is connected to one of the other bedroom so you can potential have a connecting Nursey/Office/retreat room.  Primary bathroom features standup shower, white cabinet with granite countertop. Backyard features pool with fencing for added security.  Property has plenty of parking with a long cemented driveway that could accommodate an RV and a 2 car garage. Home has new roof, new furnace, leased solar and Filtered Soft Water System. Won't Last, priced to sell!!
